snippet.title: Best VGM 2096 - Suikoden III - Beautiful Grasslands
snippet.description:
See also:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Suikoden III (2002)
Beautiful Grasslands
Michiru Yamane, Keiko Fukami & Masahiko Kimura
